NEW TUTORIAL_MILITARY_FLEET_DESC:1 "§SMilitary Fleets§! are used to protect our emerging empire from threats... or to expand our glorious rule through force of arms, if we so wish.\n\nOur current §SNavy Size§! is limited, but it can be increased by researching new technologies, owning additional §SPops§! and building §SStarbase Anchorages§!. No §SAdmiral§! has been assigned to our starting fleet, so if we have the §SEnergy Credits§! to spare we may wish to recruit one."
OLD TUTORIAL_MILITARY_FLEET_DESC:0 "§SMilitary Fleets§! are used to protect our emerging empire from threats... or to expand our glorious rule through force of arms, if we so wish.\n\nOur current §SNavy Size§! is limited, but it can be increased by researching new technologies and owning additional §SPops§! and §SSpaceports§!. No §SAdmiral§! has been assigned to our starting fleet, so if we have the §SInfluence§! points to spare we may wish to recruit one."
CN  TUTORIAL_MILITARY_FLEET_DESC:1 "§舰队§! 用于保护我们的新兴帝国免遭威胁…或按照我们的意愿，通过武力扩展我们的荣耀统治。\n\n我们当前的§S舰队规模§! 有限，但通过研究新科技、增加额外§S人口§!修建§S基地§!可以增加我们的舰队规模。未为我们的初始舰队分配§S舰队司令§!，因此，如果我们有备用的§S影响力§! 点数，我们可能希望招募一名。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_MILITARY_FLEET_DESC:1 "§舰队§! 用于保护我们的新兴帝国免遭威胁…或按照我们的意愿，通过武力扩展我们的荣耀统治。\n\n我们当前的§S舰队规模§! 有限，但通过研究新科技、增加额外§S人口§!修建§S太空基地§!可以增加我们的舰队规模。未为我们的初始舰队分配§S舰队司令§!，因此，如果我们有备用的§S能源点数§!，我们可能希望招募一名。"
NEW TUTORIAL_SCIENCE_SHIP_DESC:3 "This is our §SScience Ship§!, which is used to §SSurvey§! astronomical objects such as planets in a star system. A planet needs to be surveyed in order to make its §SResources§! visible.\n\nOur home system has already been surveyed, so we should focus our efforts elsewhere. With the Science Ship selected, open the §SGalaxy Map§!, right click on a star neighboring our home system and select §SSurvey System§!. The ship will now travel to this system and survey all of its planetary bodies."
OLD TUTORIAL_SCIENCE_SHIP_DESC:2 "This is our §SScience Ship§!, which is used to §SSurvey§! astronomical objects such as planets in a star system. A planet needs to be surveyed in order to make its §SResources§! visible.\n\nTo put it to work, simply right-click on a not-yet-surveyed planetary body and select §SSurvey System§!. The ship will then travel between all objects in the system and survey them each in turn.\n\nSurveying other planets may also uncover ones that are §SHabitable§! and ripe for future colonization."
CN  TUTORIAL_SCIENCE_SHIP_DESC:3 "这是我们的§S科研船§!，主要用于§S勘察§!诸如行星之类的天体。行星被勘察之后，才会显示蕴藏的§S资源§!。\n\n要让其工作，只要右击未被勘察的行星，选择§S$FLEETORDER_SURVEY_ALL_BUTTON$§!。科研船就会依次勘察恒星系中的各个天体。\n\n勘察其他星球时也可能会发现§S可居住§!星球，可在将来纳入殖民范畴。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_SCIENCE_SHIP_DESC:3 "这是我们的§S科研船§!，主要用于§S勘察§!星系中诸如行星之类的各个天体。行星被勘察之后，才会显示蕴藏的§S资源§!。\n\n我们家园所在的星系已经进行勘察，所以我们应该将我们的注意放到其他地方。选择科研船后，打开§S银河系地图§!，右键点击我们家园星系附近的一个星系并选择§S勘察星系§!。科研船就会依次勘察恒星系中的各个天体。"
NEW TUTORIAL_CONSTRUCTION_SHIP_DESC:1 "This is our §SConstruction Ship§!, which is used to construct space stations. When an astronomical object such as a planet has been surveyed, we can order this ship to build a §SResearch Station§! or a §SMining Station§! to exploit any resources it may have.\n\nThese ships are also used to build §SStarbases§! in unclaimed systems, making them critical to our expansion plans."
OLD TUTORIAL_CONSTRUCTION_SHIP_DESC:0 "This is our §SConstruction Ship§!, which is used to construct space stations. When an astronomical object such as a planet has been surveyed, we can order this ship to build a §SResearch Station§! or a §SMining Station§! to exploit any resources it may have.\n\nDifferent types of stations, such as §SMilitary Stations§! that can be built anywhere inside a system, will become available as our technological capability increases."
CN  TUTORIAL_CONSTRUCTION_SHIP_DESC:1 "这是我们的§S工程船§!，用于建设基地。当行星之类的天体勘察完毕后，就可以派遣工程船建造一座§S科研基地§!，也可建造§S采矿基地§!以便采集行星上的资源。\n\n不同的基地，如§S军事基地§!等，只要科技能力满足条件，就可以在星系内部任意位置进行建造了。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_CONSTRUCTION_SHIP_DESC:1 "这是我们的§S工程船§!，用于建设基地。当行星之类的天体勘察完毕后，就可以派遣工程船建造一座§S科研基地§!，也可建造§S采矿基地§!以便采集行星上的资源。\n\n这种飞船可以在没主权的星系中建造§S太空基地§!，这对我们的扩张至关重要。"
NEW TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_COMBAT_DESC:2 "This is where we manage all ground forces on this planet. The upper portion of this view is divided into three sections. The top section represents the orbital space above the planet, the middle section is the atmosphere and the bottom section is the surface.\n\nNew §SArmies§! are also raised here, by clicking §SRecruit§! in the bottom right. A limited number of §SDefense Armies§! are produced automatically by your planetary capital building as well as any additional §SStronghold§! buildings that are present and manned by a §SPop§!."
OLD TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_COMBAT_DESC:1 "This is where we manage all ground forces on this planet. The upper portion of this view is divided into three sections. The top section represents the orbital space above the planet, the middle section is the atmosphere and the bottom section is the surface.\n\nNew §SArmies§! are also raised here, by clicking §SRecruit§! in the bottom right. §SDefense Armies§! should be trained to defend our planets from possible invasions. In wartime, §SAssault Armies§! must be sent to occupy enemy planets if we wish to claim these worlds as §SWar Demands§! during peace negotiations."
CN  TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_COMBAT_DESC:2 "在这里，可以对行星上的所有地面单位进行管理。界面上方分为三个部分，最上部分为行星上方的轨道空间，中间部分为大气层，而最下部分为行星表面。\n\n单击右下方的§S招募§!按键，就可以招募新的§S部队§!。在行星上部署§S防御部队§!可以防止行星被入侵。战争时期，派遣§S进攻部队§!占领敌方行星，在和谈时就可以在§S战争诉求§!中要求吞并这些行星。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_COMBAT_DESC:2 "在这里，可以对行星上的所有地面单位进行管理。界面上方分为三个部分，最上部分为行星上方的轨道空间，中间部分为大气层，而最下部分为行星表面。\n\n单击右下方的§S招募§!按键，就可以招募新的§S部队§!。你的行星都城以及§S要塞§!等建筑会按照§S人口§!自动产生一定数量的§S防御部队§!。"
NEW TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_SPACEPORT_DESC:3 "The §SSpaceport§! tab is where we view orbiting fleets and build new civilian ships. Military ships can only be constructed at a §SStarbase§! equipped with a §SShipyard§!, but Construction, Science and Colony Ships are all built here.\n\nEven if we lose our last Starbase, we still have the means to expand and rebuild as long as we possess at least one inhabited planet."
OLD TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_SPACEPORT_DESC:2 "The §SSpaceport§! tab is where we view orbiting fleets, build new ships and upgrade the station itself. If a planet has no Spaceport, we can order the construction of one if we have the necessary §SResources§!.\n\nClick an §SEmpty Module Slot§! to view a list of available modules to install. Click the §SBuild§! button at the bottom of the Build Queue, and a list of all §SShip Designs§! and §SSpaceport Upgrades§! available for construction will appear to the right."
CN  TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_SPACEPORT_DESC:3 "§S太空港§!标签页可以查看轨道中的舰队，建造新舰船以及升级太空港。如果行星没有太空港，就可以在拥有足够§S资源§!的情况下建造一个。\n\n点击§S空模块槽§!可以查看可用的模块列表。单击建造列表底部的§S建造§!按钮，右侧就会出现一个包含全部§S舰船设计§!和可用的§S太空港升级§!的列表。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_SPACEPORT_DESC:3 "§S太空港§!标签页可以查看轨道中的舰队和建造新的民用船只。军舰只能在配备了§S船坞§!的§S太空基地§!上建造，但在这里可以建造工程船、科研船和殖民船。\n\n即便是我们失去了最后的太空基地，只要我们还拥有一个有人居住的行星，我们就有能力进行扩张和重建。"
NEW TUTORIAL_MILITARY_STATION_DESC:2 "§SMilitary Stations§! are static defenses that can be used to protect important planets or strategic avenues of approach, but can only be built within our borders or territories we have special access to.\n\nTake care not to build too many - like ships, their upkeep costs will be a drain on our economy."
OLD TUTORIAL_MILITARY_STATION_DESC:2 "§SMilitary Stations§! are static defenses that can be used to protect important planets or strategic avenues of approach, but can only be built within our borders or territories we have special access to.\n\nTake care not to build too many - like ships, their maintenance costs will be a drain on our economy."
CN  TUTORIAL_MILITARY_STATION_DESC:2 "§S军事基地§!是静态防御设施，可以用来保护重要行星或者战略枢纽。但只能在帝国境内，或有特殊使用权的区域内建造。\n\n注意不要建得太多——和舰船一样，军事基地需要维持费用。建造太多会对帝国经济造成很大压力。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_MILITARY_STATION_DESC:2 "§S军事基地§!是静态防御设施，可以用来保护重要行星或者战略枢纽。但只能在帝国境内，或有特殊使用权的区域内建造。\n\n注意不要建得太多——和舰船一样，军事基地需要维持费用。建造太多会对帝国经济造成很大压力。"
NEW TUTORIAL_MINING_STATION_DESC:2 "§SMining Stations§! are used to extract the §SMinerals§! and §SStrategic Resources§! of the object they orbit.\n\n§SMining Stations§! are not needed to access the resources of colonized planets, and can only be built within our borders."
OLD TUTORIAL_MINING_STATION_DESC:1 "§SMining Stations§! are used to extract the §SMinerals§! and §SStrategic Resources§! of the object they orbit.\n\nThese resources can then be used by §SPops§! and §SOrbital Refineries§!. §SMining Stations§! are not needed to access the resources of colonized planets, and can only be built within our borders."
CN  TUTORIAL_MINING_STATION_DESC:2 "§S采矿基地§!用于采集天体的§S矿物§!和§S战略资源§!。\n\n§S人口§!和§S轨道精炼厂§!可以使用这些资源。已被殖民的星球上的资源，不需要§S采矿基地§!就可以进行使用。采矿基地只能建造在帝国境内。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_MINING_STATION_DESC:2 "§S采矿基地§!用于采集天体的§S矿物§!和§S战略资源§!。\n\n§S采矿基地§!可以不用对行星进行殖民就可以采集资源，但是只能在我们的边境线内建造。"
NEW TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_DECISIONS_DESC:2 "The §SPolicies§! tab covers government §SPolicies§! as well as empire-wide §SEdicts§!, practices that can be enforced by spending some of our resources.\n\nThere are often a few possible stances to take for any given §SPolicy§!, though we may be limited by technology as well as our §SEthos§!."
OLD TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_DECISIONS_DESC:1 "The §SPolicies§! tab covers government §SPolicies§! as well as empire-wide §SEdicts§!, practices that can be enforced by spending some of our §SInfluence§!.\n\nThere are often a few possible stances to take for any given §SPolicy§!, though we may be limited by technology as well as our §SEthos§!."
CN  TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_DECISIONS_DESC:2 "§S政策§!标签页显示的是政府§S政策§!以及帝国§S法令§!，可以通过花费§S影响力§!来实施。\n\n对于任何§S政策§!，都会产生若干种应对态度，但某些态度可能会受到科技以及§S特征§!的限制。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_DECISIONS_DESC:2 "§S政策§!标签页显示的是政府§S政策§!以及帝国§S法令§!，可以通过花费一些我们的资源来实施。\n\n对于任何§S政策§!，都会产生若干种相应影响，但某些态度可能会受到科技以及§S特征§!的限制。"
NEW TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_TITLE:1 "Starbases"
OLD TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_TITLE:0 "Frontier Outpost"
CN  TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_TITLE:1 "边境哨站"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_TITLE:1 "太空基地"
NEW TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_DESC:3 "This is our system's §SStarbase§!. These massive space stations are the last line of defense in a system, and they are also used to produce military ships.\n\nEach system can only support a single Starbase. Building one in an uninhabited system will give us ownership of it. In the future, technologies may be unlocked that lets us upgrade Starbases further, allowing them to house an even greater number of §SModules§! and §SBuildings§!."
OLD TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_DESC:1 "The frontiers of our Empire are by no means final.\n\n§SFrontier Outposts§! act as beacons projecting our influence into the void. By building them outside our domain, we expand and demarcate our borders to claim systems for mining and research purposes."
CN  TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_DESC:3 "帝国的边界不是终结。\n\n§S边境哨站§!向虚空中投射我们的影响力。在帝国领域外建造边境哨站可以拓展我们的控制范围，让我们有更多的星系以供采掘资源和科学研究。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_DESC:3 "这个是我们星系的§S太空基地§!。这些巨大的空间站是我们星系的最后防线，它们也可以用来制造军舰。\n\n每个星系只能支撑一个太空基地。我无人控制的星系中建造它，我们的获得星系的所有权。在未来，科技可能解锁让我们进一步升级太空基地，让它们容纳更多的§S模块§!和§S建筑§!。"
ADD TUTORIAL_WAR_GOAL_TITLE:0 "War Goal"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_WAR_GOAL_TITLE:0 "战争诉求"
ADD TUTORIAL_WAR_GOAL_DESC:0 "When declaring war we also need to declare our intention, to both our enemy and any allies. This §SWar Goal§! determines what kind of demands we can press during peace negotiations, ranging from the ceding of claimed systems to vassalization.\n\nPresenting this goal gives the enemy an opportunity to react appropriately - they might give up immediately, present a counter-offer and truce, or defend their interests to the last man, woman, fungal spore or half-sapient herbivore. Finding out is part of the fun!\n\nTo declare a §SWar Goal§!, select it in the list."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_WAR_GOAL_DESC:0 "我们需要在宣战时候向我们的敌人和盟友宣布我们的意图。§S战争诉求§!决定了当进行和平谈判是我们可以提出怎样的要求，从割让星系到要求成为附庸国等一系列要求。\n\n提出这个诉求敌人作出相应的反应：他们可能立即投降、还价和休战，或者捍卫他们的利益，直到最后一个男人、女人、真菌孢子或半智慧食草动物。探索可是乐趣的一部分！\n\n要宣告一个§S战争诉求§!，可以在列表中选择它。"
ADD TUTORIAL_WAROVERVIEW_TITLE:0 "War Overview"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_WAROVERVIEW_TITLE:0 "战争概况"
ADD TUTORIAL_WAROVERVIEW_DESC:0 "This window presents an overview of our current war. Each side suffers §SWar Exhaustion§! depending on how the war is progressing, which determines how willing they are to accept a peace agreement.\n\nIf War Exhaustion reaches 100% for one side, the other side can enforce a §SStatus Quo§! agreement. The results of all engagements that have so far been fought in the war can also be tracked here."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_WAROVERVIEW_DESC:0 "这个窗口概述了我们当前的战争。取决于战争进展情况，战争各方都会产生§S厌战度§!，这决定了他们是否愿意接受和平协议。\n\n如果一方厌战度抵达100%，另一方就可以强制执行§S维持现状§!协议。迄今为止在战争中的所有冲突情况都可以在这里进行追踪查看。"
NEW TUTORIAL_EXPANSION_PLANNER_DESC:2 "In the §HExpansion Planner§! we find nearby §SHabitable§! planets that may present opportunities for colonization. We can build §SColony Ships§! and issue them orders directly from this screen.\n\nPlanets must be surveyed and any anomalies found on the planet must be researched before the planet can be colonized. A §SStarbase§! must also have been constructed in the planet's system, so that it lies within our borders."
OLD TUTORIAL_EXPANSION_PLANNER_DESC:1 "In the §HExpansion Planner§! we find nearby §SHabitable§! planets that may present opportunities for colonization. We can build §SColony Ships§! and issue them orders directly from this screen.\n\nPlanets must be surveyed and any anomalies found on the planet must be researched before the planet can be colonized."
CN  TUTORIAL_EXPANSION_PLANNER_DESC:2 "在§H扩张规划器§!中，我们能找到附近可供殖民的§S宜居§!星球。我们能直接在这个界面中建造§S殖民船§!，然后发出指令。\n\n殖民星球之前，必须先勘察星球并且研究星球上发现的异常现象。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_EXPANSION_PLANNER_DESC:2 "在§H扩张规划器§!中，我们能找到附近可供殖民的§S宜居§!星球。我们能直接在这个界面中建造§S殖民船§!，然后发出指令。\n\n殖民星球之前，必须先勘察星球并且研究星球上发现的异常现象。§S太空基地§!必须建造在行星系中，所以它就位于我们的边境线之内。"
ADD TUTORIAL_FLEET_MANAGER_TITLE:0 "Fleet Manager"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_FLEET_MANAGER_TITLE:0 "舰队管理器"
ADD TUTORIAL_FLEET_MANAGER_DESC:0 "In the §SFleet Manager§!, we can create templates for our military fleets. As our fleets grow in size, these templates make it easier to quickly order replacements for any losses they may have sustained."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_FLEET_MANAGER_DESC:0 "在§S舰队管理器§!中，我们可以为我们的军事舰队创建模板。随着我们的舰队规模壮大，这些模板更容易在舰队受到任何损失后进行快速订购替代品。"
ADD TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_VIEW_TITLE:0 "Claims"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_VIEW_TITLE:0 "领土主张"
ADD TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_VIEW_DESC:0 "Through the §SClaims§! interface, we can spend §SInfluence§! to lay claim to star systems owned by others. Having a claim on a system gives us a valid §SCasus Belli§! against the owner, allowing us to declare war for the purpose of conquering it.\n\nIn wars involving multiple allies, the empire with the highest claim on a system will be the one gaining ownership upon the successful conclusion of the war."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_VIEW_DESC:0 "通过§S领土主张§!界面，我们可以花费§S影响力§!宣称拥有其他人的星系的所有权。宣称所有权会给我们针对对星系所有者提供有效的§S战争理由§!，允许我们对其宣布的征服战争。\n\n在涉及多个盟友的战争中，最高的宣称的帝国将在战争胜利后的获得该星系。"
NEW advisor.15.desc:1 "One of our §SScience Ships§! has just surveyed a world that would make an excellent candidate for our first colony. It is of the same §Splanet class§! as our homeworld, so our colonists should be quite comfortable there.\n\nBefore we can colonize this world, however, our borders must be extended to cover the system it is in. This is accomplished by using a §SConstruction Ship§! to build a §SStarbase§! there."
OLD advisor.15.desc:0 "One of our §SScience Ships§! has just surveyed a world that would make an excellent candidate for our first colony. It is of the same §Splanet class§! as our homeworld, so our colonists should be quite comfortable there.\n\nTo colonize this world, build a §SColony Ship§! and click on §SColonize§! among its available orders. Then simply click on the planet we wish to settle on."
CN  advisor.15.desc:1 "我们的一艘§S科研船§!发现了十分适合作为我们第一块殖民地的星球。它和我们母星的§S行星种类§!相同，所以我们的殖民者应该可以很快适应。\n\n要殖民这个星球的话，先造一艘§S殖民船§!，然后点击§S殖民§!，再点击需要殖民的星球。"
CHANGE advisor.15.desc:1 "我们的一艘§S科研船§!发现了十分适合作为我们第一块殖民地的星球。它和我们母星的§S行星种类§!相同，所以我们的殖民者应该可以很快适应。\n\n但是在我们殖民这个世界之前，我们的边境线必须扩展并覆盖它所在的星系。通过§S工程船§!在这里建造§S太空基地§!可以完成这项工作。"
NEW advisor.20.desc:0 "We are losing Energy Credits at an alarming rate. Last month's budget report makes for some grim reading.\n\nSpiraling upkeep costs are a common cause of budget deficits. If this is the case, we may want to consider disbanding some of our ships, armies or stations."
OLD advisor.20.desc:0 "We are losing Energy Credits at an alarming rate. Last month's budget report makes for some grim reading.\n\nSpiraling maintenance costs are a common cause of budget deficits. If this is the case, we may want to consider disbanding some of our ships, armies or stations."
CN  advisor.20.desc:0 "我们正以可怕的速度损失能源点数，上个月的预算报表情况十分糟糕。\n\n维护费用是财政赤字的常见原因。如果不幸言中，则应该遣散一部分飞船，部队或者太空港。"
CHANGE advisor.20.desc:0 "我们正以可怕的速度损失能源点数，上个月的预算报表情况十分糟糕。\n\n维护费用是财政赤字的常见原因。如果不幸言中，则应该遣散一部分飞船，部队或者太空港。"
NEW advisor.26.desc:1 "One of our first priorities should be to survey our neighboring star systems. Their resources, and any habitable planets, will remain unknown to us until this has been accomplished.\n\nTo begin surveying, select our §SScience Ship§! and click on the §SSurvey§! order. Then go to the §SGalaxy Map§! and click on an unsurveyed system that borders our home system. Note that the ship will now move to that system and survey all of its planets in turn."
OLD advisor.26.desc:0 "One of our first priorities should be to survey all planetary bodies within our home system. Their resources will remain hidden to us until this has been accomplished.\n\nTo begin surveying, select our §SScience Ship§! and click on the §SSurvey§! order. Then click on a not surveyed planet and observe as the ship moves from planet to planet, surveying each of them in turn."
CN  advisor.26.desc:1 "我们的首要目标是勘察我方母星系里的所有天体，勘察完成之后方可了解各天体上储存的资源。\n\n要开始勘察，选择§S科研船§!，点击§S勘察§!命令，然后按次序点击未被勘察过的行星。接下来飞船便会依次进行勘察。"
CHANGE advisor.26.desc:1 "我们的首要目标是勘察我们相邻星系里的所有天体。勘察完成之后就可发现天体上储存的资源和那些可居住的行星。\n\n想要开始勘察，请选择我们的§S科研船§!并点击§S勘察§!命令。然后进入§S银河系地图§!并点击与我们家园星系相邻的未勘察星系。注意，该飞船将移动到该星系并依次勘察其中的所有行星。"
NEW tutorial.1.desc:2 "Building a star empire can be a daunting task. To help get things started, I will be providing instructional missions that cover the basic steps necessary to establish ourselves as a successful interstellar power.\n\nThe first mission is to fully survey a neighboring star system. I have added it as an entry to the §SSituation Log§!. To access it, click on the Situation Log button in the left section of the top bar or press §SF3§!."
OLD tutorial.1.desc:1 "Building a star empire can be a daunting task. To help get things started, I will be providing instructional missions that cover the basic steps necessary to establish ourselves as a successful interstellar power.\n\nThe first mission is to fully survey our home system. I have added it as an entry to the §SSituation Log§!. To access it, click on the Situation Log button in the left section of the top bar or press §SF3§!."
CN  tutorial.1.desc:2 "建造恒星帝国或许看起来不是一件易事。为了保证你早日走上正轨，就由我来提供一系列指导任务，顺便简单介绍一下如何成功地建造庞大的跨星系势力。\n\n第一个任务自然是完成对母星系的全地图探索。已经将这个任务加入到§S情报日志§!啦。想要查看任务的话，就请按下屏幕左上角的情报日志按键，或者直接使用键盘§SF3§!吧。"
CHANGE tutorial.1.desc:2 "建造恒星帝国或许看起来不是一件易事。为了保证你早日走上正轨，就由我来提供一系列指导任务，顺便简单介绍一下如何成功地建造庞大的跨星系势力。\n\n第一个任务是完成对一个相邻星系的全面勘察。我已经将任务作为一项添加到§S情报日志§!中。要查看他，请点击顶部栏目左边的情报日志按钮或者直接使用键盘§SF3§!键。"
