NEW tutorial.76.desc:1 "Excellent. As you can see on the §SGalaxy Map§!, the borders of our empire have expanded to include the system where we built our new Starbase."
OLD tutorial.76.desc:0 "Far out. That is where the frontiers of our domain now lie."
CN  tutorial.76.desc:1 "很棒。新的疆域就定在此处。"
CHANGE tutorial.76.desc:1 "太好了。正如你在§S银河系地图§!上看到的那样，我们的帝国边境线已经扩展到我们新建的太空基地所在的星系。"
