NEW tutorial_1_chain_desc:3 "We need to explore our neighboring star systems. To do this, select our §SScience Ship§! - either by clicking on the ship itself, or by selecting the vessel in the §SOutliner§!.\n\nThen click on the §SSurvey§! button in the fleet interface, open the §SGalaxy Map§! and select a non-surveyed system with a hyperlane connection to our home system. Our Science Ship will now plot a course to survey all planetary bodies within this system."
OLD tutorial_1_chain_desc:2 "We need to fully explore our home system before venturing out into the galaxy. To do this, select our §SScience Ship§! - either by clicking on the ship itself, or by selecting the vessel in the §SOutliner§!.\n\nThen click on the §SSurvey§! button in the fleet interface, and select a non-surveyed planet near your homeworld. Your Science Ship will now plot a course to survey all planetary bodies within the system."
CN  tutorial_1_chain_desc:3 "在我们进军宇宙之前，必须充分探索我们的母星系。为此，需要选择我们的 §S科研船§!——点击飞船或者在§S概览窗口§!中选择飞船。\n\n然后在舰队界面点击§S勘察§!按钮，选择一个在你母星附近还没有勘察过的星球。你的科研船会自动对星系内的所有天体进行勘察。"
CHANGE tutorial_1_chain_desc:3 "我们需要探索我们邻居的星系。为此，请选择我们的§S科研船§!——无论是点击飞船本身，还是通过§S信息缩略表§!选择船只。\n\n然后点击舰队界面的§S勘察§!按钮，打开§S银河系地图§!并选择一个与母星系有着超空间航道相连的未勘察星系。我们的科研船绘制出一个路线来勘察该星系中的所有星体。"
