NEW tutorial_3_chain_desc:1 "We will need a §SConstruction Ship§! if we are to exploit the resources that are discovered by our §SScience Ship§!.\n\nCivilian ships like §SScience Ships§! do not require a §SStarbase§! and can be built planetside. Click on [Root.Capital.GetName] and select the §SSpaceport§! tab. Then click on the §SBuild§! button, and select §SConstruction Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SMinerals§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
OLD tutorial_3_chain_desc:0 "We will need a §SConstruction Ship§! if we are to exploit the resources that are discovered by our §SScience Ship§!.\n\nTo build one, you need to access the §SSpaceport§! that orbits [Root.Capital.GetName]. Either click on it directly, or select the Spaceport tab in our homeworld's planet interface. Then click on the §SBuild§! button, and select §SConstruction Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SMinerals§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
CN  tutorial_3_chain_desc:1 "如果要开采 §S科研船§!发现的资源，就需要一艘 §S工程船§!。\n\n要建造一艘工程船，需要进入[Root.Capital.GetName]轨道上的§S太空港§!。直接点击或者在母星星球界面选择太空港标签，然后点击§S建造§!按钮，选择 §S工程船§!。\n\n注意，需要有足够的§S矿物§!才能建造工程船。"
CHANGE tutorial_3_chain_desc:1 "如果要开采 §S科研船§!发现的资源，就需要一艘 §S工程船§!。\n\像§S工程船§!这样的民用船只不需要§S太空基地§!，由行星直接建造。点击[Root.Capital.GetName]并选择§S太空港§!标签。然后点击§S建造§!按钮，并从可选项中选择§S工程船§!。\n\n注意，需要有足够的§S矿物§!才能建造工程船。"
NEW tutorial_9_chain_desc:2 "We should consider building a second §SScience Ship§! to increase the speed at which we survey our region of the galaxy.\n\nCivilian ships like §SScience Ships§! do not require a §SStarbase§! and can be built planetside. Click on [Root.Capital.GetName] and select the §SSpaceport§! tab. Then click on the §SBuild§! button, and select §SScience Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SMinerals§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
OLD tutorial_9_chain_desc:0 "We should consider building a second §SScience Ship§! to increase the speed at which we survey our region of the galaxy.\n\nTo do this, access the §SSpaceport§! orbiting our homeworld. Either click on it directly, or select the Spaceport tab from our homeworld's planet interface. Then click on the §SBuild§! button and select §SScience Ship§! from among the available options."
CN  tutorial_9_chain_desc:2 "我们应该考虑建造第二艘 §S科研船§!，以便增加我们探索宇宙的速度。\n\n要进行建造，请进入母星轨道上的§S太空港§!。你可以直接点击太空港或者在母星界面上选择太空港标签，然后点击§S建造§!按钮并选择 §S科研船§!。"
CHANGE tutorial_9_chain_desc:2 "我们应该考虑建造第二艘 §S科研船§!，以便增加我们探索宇宙的速度。\n\n像§S科研船§!这样的民用船只不需要§S太空基地§!，由行星直接建造。点击[Root.Capital.GetName]并选择§S太空港§!标签。然后点击§S建造§!按钮，并从可选项中选择§S科研船§!。\n\n注意，需要有足够的§S矿物§!才能建造工程船。"
NEW tutorial_10_chain_desc:1 "We may want to consider recruiting another §SScientist§! to command our new §SScience Ship§!. A Science Ship cannot perform survey missions or research §SAnomalies§! without a Scientist.\n\nSelect our new Science Ship, and then click on the §SAssign Leader§! box. The §SLeaders§! tab will open, showing all Scientists currently employed by us. Click on the §SRecruit§! button at the top of this list.\n\nSelect the candidate you want, and click on their associated §SRecruit§! button. Recruiting a Leader costs §SEnergy Credits§!, and you may need to wait until you have enough stored.\n\nOnce recruited, the new Scientist will be ready for assignment on our homeworld."
OLD tutorial_10_chain_desc:0 "We may want to consider recruiting another §SScientist§! to command our new §SScience Ship§!. Although a Science Ship can still perform survey missions without a Scientist, they are unable to research §SAnomalies§!.\n\nSelect our new Science Ship, and then click on the §SAssign Leader§! box. The §SLeaders§! tab will open, showing all Scientists currently employed by us. Click on the §SRecruit§! button at the top of this list.\n\nSelect the candidate you want, and click on their associated §SRecruit§! button. Recruiting a Leader costs §SInfluence§!, and you may need to wait until you have enough stored.\n\nOnce recruited, the new Scientist will be ready for assignment on our homeworld."
CN  tutorial_10_chain_desc:1 "我们或许应当考虑雇佣另外一名§S科学家§!指挥新§S科研船§!。虽然科研船可以在无科学家时继续勘察，但是失去了科学家的指导，他们便无法研究§S异常现象§!。\n\n选择我们新的科研船，点击§S指派领袖§!。§S领袖§!页面会展开，展示为我们服务的所有科学家。在列表顶部点击§S招募§!按钮。\n\n选择你想要的科学家，然后点击§S招募§!按钮。招募领导会花费§S影响力§!，请务必储存足够。\n\n招募完毕后，新的科学家便会在母星中等待部署。"
CHANGE tutorial_10_chain_desc:1 "我们应当考虑雇佣另外一名§S科学家§!指挥新§S科研船§!。科研船无法在没有科学家的情况下执行勘察任务或研究§S异常现象§! 。\n\n选择我们新的科研船，点击§S指派领袖§!。§S领袖§!页面会展开，展示为我们服务的所有科学家。在列表顶部点击§S招募§!按钮。\n\n选择你想要的科学家，然后点击§S招募§!按钮。招募领导会花费§S能量点数§!，请务必储存足够。\n\n招募完毕后，新的科学家便会在母星中等待部署。"
NEW tutorial_11_chain_desc:2 "The time has come to colonize another world. First we will have to build a §SColony Ship§!. These ships take a long time to build and require a large amount of §SMinerals§!, but a thriving colony will more than return on this investment.\n\nCivilian ships like §SColony Ships§! do not require a §SStarbase§! and can be built planetside. Click on [Root.Capital.GetName] and select the §SSpaceport§! tab. Then click on the §SBuild§! button, and select §SColony Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SMinerals§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
OLD tutorial_11_chain_desc:0 "The time has come to colonize another world. First we will have to build a §SColony Ship§!. These ships take a long time to build and require a large amount of §SMinerals§!, but a thriving colony will more than return on this investment.\n\nTo build a Colony Ship, go into the §SSpaceport§! tab of your homeworld. Click on the §SBuild§! button and select Colony Ship from among the available options when you have sufficient Minerals.\n\nAnother window will now appear, prompting you to select the species and ethics of the colonists that will be carried within the ship. Pick the one you prefer, and construction of the ship will begin."
CN  tutorial_11_chain_desc:2 "是时候去殖民下一个星球了。首先我们要建造一艘§S殖民船§!。这些飞船将会耗费大量时间和§S矿物§!，但是建立的殖民地发达后就能得到比投资多得多的回报。\n\n要建造殖民船，需要到母星的§S太空港§!页面中，点击§S建造§!按钮，收集足够的矿物后，在可用选项中选择殖民船。\n\n此时会出现另一个窗口，向你询问这艘殖民船上要搭载殖民者的种族与道德体系。选择想要的选项后，船只便会开始建造。"
CHANGE tutorial_11_chain_desc:2 "是时候去殖民下一个星球了。首先我们要建造一艘§S殖民船§!。这些飞船将会耗费大量时间和§S矿物§!，但是建立的殖民地发达后就能得到比投资多得多的回报。\n\n像§S殖民船§!这样的民用船只不需要§S太空基地§!，由行星直接建造。点击[Root.Capital.GetName]并选择§S太空港§!标签。然后点击§S建造§!按钮，并从可选项中选择§S殖民船§!。\n\n请注意，你需要在开始前为建造飞船积累足够的§S矿物§!。"
NEW tutorial_12_chain_desc:1 "We should now use our new §SColony Ship§! to establish our first colony. The best planetary candidates are those that are of the same planet class as our homeworld - our colonists will have no problems adjusting to their environments.\n\nTo colonize a planet, click on your Colony Ship or select it in the §SOutliner§!. Then click on the §SColonize§! button in its fleet interface, and select the planet you want to colonize. Note that you can only colonize planets that have been surveyed, that have no §SAnomalies§! and that you have researched the necessary technology for. They must also be located within your borders.\n\nWhen you have selected an appropriate planet, you will be prompted to place your first colony building on a tile. As soon as you have done this, your Colony Ship will blast off to establish our new colony."
OLD tutorial_12_chain_desc:0 "We should now use our new §SColony Ship§! to establish our first colony. The best planetary candidates are those that are of the same planet class as our homeworld - our colonists will have no problems adjusting to their environments.\n\nTo colonize a planet, click on your Colony Ship or select it in the §SOutliner§!. Then click on the §SColonize§! button in its fleet interface, and select the planet you want to colonize. Note that you can only colonize planets that have been surveyed, that have no §SAnomalies§! and that you have researched the necessary technology for.\n\nWhen you have selected an appropriate planet, you will be prompted to place your first colony building on a tile. As soon as you have done this, your Colony Ship will blast off to establish our new colony."
CN  tutorial_12_chain_desc:1 "接下来，就该使用新造的§S殖民船§!建立我们的第一个殖民地了。最佳的殖民星球应该是和我们母星环境差不多的星球，这样殖民者就不会有适应环境的问题。\n\n要对星球进行殖民，点击你的殖民船或者在§S概览窗口§!选择飞船，然后在飞船的船队界面点击§S殖民§!按钮，选择想要殖民的星球。注意，你只能对已勘察过，没有§S异常现象§!，并已研究相关科技的星球进行殖民。\n\n选择一个合适的星球后，则要选择放置第一个殖民建筑的地块。完成这些后，你的殖民船就会马上开始建立新的殖民地。"
CHANGE tutorial_12_chain_desc:1 "接下来，就该使用新造的§S殖民船§!建立我们的第一个殖民地了。最佳的殖民星球应该是和我们母星环境差不多的星球，这样殖民者就不会有适应环境的问题。\n\n要对星球进行殖民，点击你的殖民船或者在§S信息缩略表§!选择飞船，然后在飞船的船队界面点击§S殖民§!按钮，选择想要殖民的星球。注意，你只能对已勘察过，没有§S异常现象§!，并已研究相关科技的星球进行殖民。它们也位于你的边境线之内。\n\n选择一个合适的星球后，则要选择放置第一个殖民建筑的地块。完成这些后，你的殖民船就会马上开始建立新的殖民地。"
NEW tutorial_16_chain_desc:2 "We must build up a potent starfleet to ensure the security of the [Root.GetName].\n\nWith the resources now at our disposal, we shouldn't have any problems building at least five more §SCorvettes§!. Build the ships at a §SStarbase§! when our §SMineral§! supplies permit. New military ships always join any existing fleets that orbit the star of the §SStarbase§! that builds them.\n\nAlso be sure to recruit and assign an §SAdmiral§! to our new fleet. This works in the same way as assigning §SScientists§! to a §SScience Ship§! - click on the §SAssign Leader§! box in the fleet interface, and recruit a new Admiral from there. A skilled Admiral commanding a fleet can increase its performance dramatically."
OLD tutorial_16_chain_desc:1 "We must build up a potent starfleet to ensure the security of the [Root.GetName].\n\nWith the resources now at our disposal, we shouldn't have any problems building at least five more §SCorvettes§!. Build the ships at a §SSpaceport§! when our §SMineral§! supplies permit. New military ships always join any existing fleets that orbit the planet of the Spaceport that builds them.\n\nAlso be sure to recruit and assign an §SAdmiral§! to our new fleet. This works in the same way as assigning §SScientists§! to a §SScience Ship§! - click on the §SAssign Leader§! box in the fleet interface, and recruit a new Admiral from there. A skilled Admiral commanding a fleet can increase its performance dramatically."
CN  tutorial_16_chain_desc:2 "我们必须打造一支强有力的星际舰队，以保卫[Root.GetName]的安全。\n\n考虑到目前拥有的资源数量，再建造五艘§S护卫舰§!是绝不成问题的。在§S矿物§!补给允许的情况下，在§S太空港§!建造船只。新建造的军舰都将自动加入生产该军舰的太空港所在星球上存在的舰队。\n\n不要忘记为我们的新舰队指派一位§S舰队司令§!。这一过程与将§S科学家§!指派到§S科研船§!的过程并无两样——点击舰队界面的§S指派领袖§!，便可为舰队指派舰队司令。在经验丰富的舰队司令指挥下，舰队的战斗表现将有飞跃性的提升。"
CHANGE tutorial_16_chain_desc:2 我们必须打造一支强有力的星际舰队，以保卫[Root.GetName]的安全。\n\n考虑到目前拥有的资源数量，再建造五艘§S护卫舰§!是绝不成问题的。在§S矿物§!补给允许的情况下，在§S太空基地§!建造船只。新建造的军舰都将自动加入生产该军舰的§S太空基地§!所在恒星轨道上的舰队。\n\n不要忘记为我们的新舰队指派一位§S舰队司令§!。这一过程与将§S科学家§!指派到§S科研船§!的过程并无两样——点击舰队界面的§S指派领袖§!，便可为舰队指派舰队司令。在经验丰富的舰队司令指挥下，舰队的战斗表现将有飞跃性的提升。"
NEW tutorial_19_chain_desc:2 "To create a new ship design, go into the §SShip Designer§! by clicking on its associated icon in the top bar's drop-down menu, or press §SF10§!. Click on the §SNew Design§! button, and select §SCorvette§! when you are prompted to select a §SHull Size§!. The next step is to pick a §SSection§! for the design by clicking on the §SNo Section§! button at the top of the window.\n\nCorvettes are the smallest type of warship, and they are made up of only a single section unlike larger vessels. Sections determine the amount of §SWeapon§! and §SUtility§! slots on a ship. Pick one, and then start filling up the available slots with components. Make sure that the components do not exceed the power output of the reactor - a ship's power supply cannot be in the negative.\n\nIf you want to make things easy, simply click on the §SAuto-complete Ship§! button and the game will finish the design for you."
OLD tutorial_19_chain_desc:1 "To create a new ship design, go into the §SShip Designer§! by clicking on its associated icon in the top bar's drop-down menu, or press §SF10§!. Click on the §SNew Design§! button, and select §SCorvette§! when you are prompted to select a §SHull Size§!. The next step is to pick a §SSection§! for the design by clicking on the §SNo Section§! button at the top of the window.\n\nCorvettes are the smallest type of warship, and they are made up of only a single section unlike larger vessels. Sections determine the amount of §SWeapon§! and §SUtility§! slots on a ship. Pick one, and then start filling up the available slots with components. Don't forget to add §SFission Reactors§! - a ship's power supply cannot be in the negative.\n\nIf you want to make things easy, simply click on the §SAuto-complete Ship§! button and the game will finish the design for you."
CN  tutorial_19_chain_desc:2 "如果想要新建船只设计，点击屏幕顶部的下拉菜单或者按下§SF10§!键前往§S舰船设计器§!界面。点击§S新设计§!键，在出现选择§S船体尺寸§!时，选择§S护卫舰§!。下一步，点击窗口上方的§S未选区块§!按钮，以为新设计选择§S区块设计§!。\n\n护卫舰是体形最小的战舰，不像大型船只，只由单一模块构成。模块决定了船只的§S武器§!和§S设施§!栏位数量。选择一个栏位，并使用组件填充可用的栏位。不要忘记添加§S裂变反应堆§!——舰船的能源供应必须保持为正数。\n\n如果想简单一些，只要点击§S自动完成舰船§!键，游戏就会帮你完成设计。"
