CHANGE advisor.1.desc_02:1 "你好，总统女士。\n\n我是VIR——原型合成智能。我的工作是在漫漫星系中为您提供建议和协助。\n\n$advisor.1.desc_filler$"
RM  TUTORIAL_WAROVERVIEW_NEGOTIATION_DESC:0 "We may at any time use our accumulated §SWarscore§! to press §Sdemands§! for our various §SWar Goals§!. Keep in mind that the enemy is unlikely to accept any demands for War Goals where the §SCost§! exceeds the Warscore we have accumulated.\n\nAdditionally, a potential victor might even show mercy by offering §SWhite Peace§!, while a likely loser may propose an unconditional §SSurrender§! to avoid spilling any more of the multitude of vital bodily fluids organics need to operate efficiently."
RM  TUTORIAL_WAROVERVIEW_STATUS_TITLE:0 "War Status"
RM  TUTORIAL_WAROVERVIEW_NEGOTIATION_TITLE:0 "War Negotiation"
RM  TUTORIAL_WARDEMANDS_DESC:2 "When declaring war we also need to declare our intentions, to both our enemy and any allies. These §SWar Goals§! determine what kind of §SDemands§! we can press during peace negotiations, ranging from the ceding of planets to vassalization.\n\nPresenting these goals gives the enemy an opportunity to react appropriately - they might give up immediately, present a counter-offer and truce, or defend their interests to the last man, woman, fungal spore or half-sapient herbivore. Finding out is part of the fun!\n\nTo declare a §SWar Goal§!, click and drag it from the list and drop it onto your §SEmpire§!, or any allied Empire of your choice."
RM  TUTORIAL_WAROVERVIEW_STATUS_DESC:0 "The §SWar Status§! screen shows the current state of any ongoing galactic conflict that we are involved in. The §SWarscore§! bar is a general representation of the two sides' military successes relative to each other, with a detailed breakdown of generated §SWarscore§! beneath."
RM  TUTORIAL_WARDEMANDS_TITLE:0 "War Demands"
